# Comments Performance Ledger

Append-only. Every published post → 7 pinned comments → 7-day score per slot.

**Schema (one row per comment per scoring event):**
```
| date_scored | post_id | comment_idx | pattern | preview | reactions | replies | score | quartile | notes |
```
- `comment_idx` — 1–7 (slot per `post` skill): 1=engagement-question · 2=tldr · 3=cta · 4=social-proof · 5=conv-extender · 6=why-i-do-this · 7=repost-amplifier
- `pattern` — short label of the phrasing used
- `score` — `reactions + (replies × 5)` (replies = thread alive, weighted heavier)
- `quartile` — blank on append; filled by `score-posts`

**Quartiles activate at ≥12 rows per slot.** Below that, `post` uses default templates.

| date_scored | post_id | comment_idx | pattern | preview | reactions | replies | score | quartile | notes |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|

